result.execSummary:
The defendant William S Whiting was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. William S Whiting is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • William S Whiting was found guilty of 4th Degree Sexual Assault, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.225(3m).
